# Omega AI Studio

Omega AI Studio is a platform that uses AI agents to plan, build, test, and deploy software.

## Features

- AI development agents
- Automated coding
- Git integration
- Task orchestration
- Project dashboard

## Agents

- Governor Agent – plans development
- Creator Agent – writes code
- Launcher Agent – runs builds/tests
- Guardian Agent – checks security

## Tech Stack

- Next.js
- Node.js
- PostgreSQL
- Prisma
